A Lake
Between strong and tall pine trees you find a sanctuary-like place. The gelid waters of a big lake are so still and quiet they perfectly display a reflection of the snowy mountains around it and the blue, cloudy sky above it. Near the lake you see some paws footsteps.
You can see a footsteps.
You can go Outside or the Mountains.
> go cave

> go cave
You follow the trail of the footsteps to the cave.

A cave
You find yourself at the entrance of a dark cave and yell: "Is anyone there?". You can only hear the echo of your voice. At the floor, near you, though, you see a torchlight.
You can see a torch.
You can go lake.
> take torch

> take torch
You grab the torchlight. It's currently switched off and not emmitting any light.
> switch on torch

> switch on torch
You switch on the torchlight and it illuminates the cave. Now you can see the stalactites... and a big grey dog sitting on the ground.
> use dog biscuit on rex

> use dog biscuit on rex

You show him the dog biscuit and his tail starts to wag. He eats it all at once and looks at you expectantly for more. You think you're friends now!
Rex is now following you.
